{
  "stem": "22582.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When the Germans came in, I understand, because I was not there, they-- they-- they were pretty rough.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they burned the-- the-- the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When someone-- when I came in, they synagogue was completely destroyed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had a very big synagogue, one of the biggest in-- in Poland with a big steel-- steel dome.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they destroyed it completely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- so-- But they let people-- they were not organized yet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They still-- the people had to-- they couldn't walk on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They couldn't walk-- they couldn't do business-- they-- be in business.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But somehow, it was no-- they didn't-- they were shooting once in awhile, but it was-- it was not organized yet.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Anyway, I went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I-- I thought that they wanted to send us back to Russia in-- at that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was registration to go to Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they were sending to the-- to the-- people were saying that they are sending to the coal mines in-- in Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I decided to go back to-- to the family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I came in the beginning of January, 1940, back to Tarnow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, the first-- the first impression was very scary because everybody had to wear this-- this armband to-- in order-- to identify that you are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you couldn't walk on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't walk here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was pretty scary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I guess I slowly acclimatized as long as you didn't-- they didn't-- at that time, they didn't kill yet, so-- I mean, it was not organized killing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was sporadic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I started-- my-- my brother-in-law, my sister's husband, was a dentist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody was supposed to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was supposed to be occupied.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
